### **âœ… 1. `@ViewScoped` ì‚¬ìš© (ê¶Œì¥)**  
í˜ì´ì§• ë²„íŠ¼ì„ ëˆŒëŸ¬ë„ `userList`ê°€ ìœ ì§€ë˜ë„ë¡ **`@ViewScoped`ë¡œ ë³€ê²½**í•˜ë©´ í•´ê²°ë©ë‹ˆë‹¤.  

#### **ğŸ”¹ `UserBean.java`**
```java
import javax.faces.view.ViewScoped;
import javax.inject.Named;
import java.io.Serializable;
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;

@Named
@ViewScoped  // ğŸ”¥ ViewScoped ì‚¬ìš© â†’ AJAX ìš”ì²­ìœ¼ë¡œ ë°ì´í„° ìœ ì§€ ê°€ëŠ¥
public class UserBean implements Serializable {
    private List<User> userList = new ArrayList<>();
    private int currentPage = 1;
    private int pageSize = 10;

    public void searchUsers() {
        int offset = (currentPage - 1) * pageSize;
        userList = userMapper.searchUsers(offset, pageSize);
    }

    public void nextPage() {
        currentPage++;
        searchUsers();
    }

    public void previousPage() {
        currentPage--;
        searchUsers();
    }

    public List<User> getUserList() { return userList; }
    public int getCurrentPage() { return currentPage; }
}
```
- `@ViewScoped` ë•ë¶„ì— **ê²€ìƒ‰ ê²°ê³¼ê°€ ìœ ì§€ë˜ê³ , í˜ì´ì§• ë²„íŠ¼(`>`, `>>`)ë„ ì •ìƒ ë™ì‘**í•©ë‹ˆë‹¤.

